  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*PsiLeft[λ1,λ2][M,n]: on-demand accessor over the memoized TauEigensystemLeft cache, same\n  bounds/spurious-guard pattern as Psi (Section B).*)\nClearAll[PsiLeft];\nPsiLeft::bnds = \"Invalid indices (M,n)=(`1`,`2`) for (λ1,λ2)=(`3`,`4`): need M an integer in 0..λ1+λ2 and n an integer in 0..M.\";\nPsiLeft::spurious = \"No genuine state at (M,n)=(`1`,`2`) for (λ1,λ2)=(`3`,`4`): weight sector M=`1` has only `5` genuine state(s) (n=0..`6`), so n=`2` does not exist.\";\nPsiLeft[λ1_, λ2_][M_, n_] := Module[{tab, mult},\n  If[! (IntegerQ[M] && IntegerQ[n] && 0 <= M <= λ1 + λ2 && 0 <= n <= M),\n    Message[PsiLeft::bnds, M, n, λ1, λ2]; Return[$Failed]];\n  tab = TauEigensystemLeft[λ1, λ2];\n  mult = dPred[M, λ1, λ2];\n  If[n > mult - 1,\n    Message[PsiLeft::spurious, M, n, λ1, λ2, mult, mult - 1]; Return[Missing[\"NoState\", {λ1, λ2, M, n}]]];\n  tab[{M, n}]];\n(*smoke test: a valid state's left eigenvector, plus confirming its last component is exactly 1*)\n{PsiLeft[2, 1][1, 0][[-1]], Length[PsiLeft[2, 1][1, 0]]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352969\" data-output-id=\"170\" data-out-n=\"138\" data-sub-idx=\"6\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"50\" data-sub-start=\"14\" data-sub-end=\"14\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[138]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrns6r4n-7s1x0sl\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezEuMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAsNlxyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1.00000000000000000000000000000</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">6</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[138]= \\left\\{1.00000000000000000000000000000,6\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
