  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*Section F — functional CG overlap. Sets up the length-1 FSoV measure/bracket (Section C's\n  mu[...][1] stripped of all site-2 factors and the cross-site (1-Exp[...]) term), normalized so\n  br1[λ1][f] = f(θ1) + (higher-tower). Then builds the functional object FLdet = det1[λ1][k^(u/h) Q1]\n  (the 1-site FSoV DETERMINANT, not the bare bracket — see cell below) and the operatorial CG\n  overlap OP = (⟨x0|g(k)⊗⟨x0|)·Psi, and gives the discovered dictionary {generator, φ(k), scalar}\n  relating them, validated as a hard assert across the full (λ1,λ2) rep sweep.\n  NOTE: Q1 carries κ1^(u/h), so k^(u/h) Q1 = (k κ1)^(u/h) q_n(u): the LHS prefactor is (k κ1)^(θ1/h),\n  which the 1/f(θ1) determinant normalization exactly cancels, leaving a clean polynomial in k.\n  See docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-16-xxx-sov-factorization-functional-overlap-design.md.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Length-1 FSoV measure and bracket. mu1 is a single-site rational measure with simple poles at\n  the tower θ1+h k, k=0..λ. Nn1 is DERIVED (not guessed) by forcing the θ1-node weight\n  w_0 = 2πI Res[mu1, θ1] to equal 1, so that br1[λ][f] = f(θ1) + (higher-tower). br1 is the residue\n  sum over the whole tower. (For λ≥1 the residues of mu1 sum to 0, so br1[λ][1]=0 — the correct\n  normalization statement is w_0=1, checked next.)*)\nClearAll[Nn1, mu1, br1];\nNn1[λ_] := Nn1[λ] = Module[{uu}, 1/(2 π I Residue[1/Product[(uu - θ1 - h k), {k, 0, λ}], {uu, θ1}])];\nmu1[λ_][u_] := Nn1[λ]/Product[(u - θ1 - h k), {k, 0, λ}];\nbr1[λ_][f_] := 2 π I Plus @@ (Residue[f mu1[λ][u], {u, #}] & /@ Table[θ1 + h k, {k, 0, λ}]);",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Internal check: the leading (θ1-node) weight must be exactly 1 for λ=1,2,3 (this IS the\n  br1[f]=f(θ1)+... normalization), and br1[λ][1] must be 0 (rational-measure residues sum to\n  zero). Also list the full weight vectors w_j for the record.*)\nw1[λ_] := Table[2 π I Residue[mu1[λ][u], {u, θ1 + h j}], {j, 0, λ}];\nNn1Check::badlead = \"Leading weight w_0 ≠ 1 for λ=`1`: w_0=`2`.\";\nNn1Check::badsum = \"br1[λ][1] ≠ 0 for λ=`1`: got `2`.\";\nDo[\n  Module[{w = w1[λ], s},\n   If[Abs[N[w[[1]] - 1]] > 10^-15, Message[Nn1Check::badlead, λ, w[[1]]]; Abort[]];\n   s = br1[λ][1];\n   If[Abs[N[s]] > 10^-15, Message[Nn1Check::badsum, λ, s]; Abort[]]],\n  {λ, 1, 3}];\n<|\"w_0 (λ=1,2,3)\" -> Table[w1[λ][[1]], {λ, 1, 3}],\n  \"full weights w_j\" -> Table[λ -> w1[λ], {λ, 1, 3}],\n  \"br1[λ][1] (λ=1,2,3)\" -> Table[br1[λ][1], {λ, 1, 3}]|>",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352969\" data-output-id=\"179\" data-out-n=\"185\" data-sub-idx=\"5\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"64\" data-sub-start=\"12\" data-sub-end=\"14\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[185]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrns6vto-fchvmpz\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.06em;vertical-align:-0.31em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">⟨</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:-0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">∣</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">w_0 (</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">=1,2,3)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.06em;vertical-align:-0.31em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">full weights w_j</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">br1[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">][1] (</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">=1,2,3)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mclose\">∣</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:-0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">⟩</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[185]= \\langle\\!\\lvert \\text{w\\_0 ($\\lambda$=1,2,3)}\\to \\left\\{1,1,1\\right\\},\\text{full weights w\\_j}\\to \\left\\{1\\to \\left\\{1,-1\\right\\},2\\to \\left\\{1,-2,1\\right\\},3\\to \\left\\{1,-3,3,-1\\right\\}\\right\\},\\text{br1[$\\lambda$][1] ($\\lambda$=1,2,3)}\\to \\left\\{0,0,0\\right\\}\\rvert\\!\\rangle",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "984faf19-2163-4d0a-b6fb-db1f9c5065d5"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Sanity: br1 acting on a generic analytic f reproduces the weighted tower sum Σ_j w_j f(θ1+h j),\n  and picks out f(θ1) as the leading term. Test with f=g[u] (undefined head, stays symbolic).*)\nClear[g];\n{br1[1][g[u]] - Sum[w1[1][[j + 1]] g[θ1 + h j], {j, 0, 1}] // Simplify,\n br1[2][g[u]] - Sum[w1[2][[j + 1]] g[θ1 + h j], {j, 0, 2}] // Simplify}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352969\" data-output-id=\"180\" data-out-n=\"187\" data-sub-idx=\"2\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"65\" data-sub-start=\"3\" data-sub-end=\"4\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[187]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrns6w7f-1cak33t\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezAsMFxyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[187]= \\left\\{0,0\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "31350aeb-dac1-4322-9fe1-98b72389b071"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*RHS operatorial CG overlap: rotate the site-1 pseudovacuum covector by g=exp[φ Ee[λ1][a,b]]\n  (Ee[a,b] nilpotent of order ≤λ1+1 on the finite-dim rep). Build g as the explicit truncated\n  series Σ_{m=0}^{λ} φ^m/m! Ee[a,b]^m — this is EXACT (higher powers vanish) and guaranteed to be a\n  polynomial in φ, avoiding MatrixExp returning an unevaluated symbolic exponential. Tensor with the\n  site-2 pseudovacuum covector, contract with the two-site right eigenvector Psi. Shapes:\n  (1×n1).(n1×n1)=1×n1 → KroneckerProduct with 1×n2 → Flatten to length D → .Psi = scalar.\n  NOTE (kernel quirk, not a typo): MatrixPower[singularMatrix,0] does NOT auto-reduce to\n  IdentityMatrix in this kernel (fires MatrixPower::sing and stays unevaluated) even though m=0 is\n  a concrete nonnegative integer, while m>=1 evaluates cleanly. Ee[λ][a,b] is nilpotent/singular for\n  the generators used here, so the m=0 identity term is split off explicitly and only\n  MatrixPower is summed over m=1..λ, which evaluates without any message.*)\nClearAll[gRot, OP];\ngRot[λ_][a_, b_][φ_] := IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ, 0}]] + Sum[φ^m/m! MatrixPower[Ee[λ][a, b], m], {m, 1, λ}];\nOP[λ1_, λ2_][a_, b_][M_, n_][φ_] := Flatten[KroneckerProduct[xSingle[λ1][{0}] . gRot[λ1][a, b][φ], xSingle[λ2][{0}]]] . Psi[λ1, λ2][M, n];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Which single-site generator is nontrivial? The lowest-weight covector ⟨x0| annihilates one of\n  E12/E21 (giving φ-independent OP); keep the other. Test on (λ1,λ2)=(2,1), state (1,0).*)\nop12 = OP[2, 1][1, 2][1, 0][φ] // Simplify;\nop21 = OP[2, 1][2, 1][1, 0][φ] // Simplify;\ngenNontrivial = Which[\n   !FreeQ[op12, φ] && FreeQ[op21, φ], {1, 2},\n   !FreeQ[op21, φ] && FreeQ[op12, φ], {2, 1},\n   True, {1, 2}  (* fallback: if both depend on φ, default to {1,2} and flag in the report *)];\n<|\"OP(E12)\" -> op12, \"OP(E21)\" -> op21, \"nontrivial generator {a,b}\" -> genNontrivial,\n  \"both φ-dependent?\" -> (!FreeQ[op12, φ] && !FreeQ[op21, φ])|>",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352969\" data-output-id=\"181\" data-out-n=\"194\" data-sub-idx=\"4\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"67\" data-sub-start=\"8\" data-sub-end=\"9\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[194]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrns6wzc-2n5idd1\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">⟨</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:-0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">∣</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">OP(E12)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.1141em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">30</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">OP(E21)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.1141em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">0.03626734060947795145020244939</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2.004237714666237867354326095</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">φ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">1.522150083623538480912456055</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.2442047957313920727733393355</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">φ</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.2141em;vertical-align:-0.35em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord\">1.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">30</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">)</span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">nontrivial generator {a,b}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">both </span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">φ</span><span class=\"mord\">-dependent?</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">False</span></span><span class=\"mclose\">∣</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:-0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">⟩</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[194]= \\langle\\!\\lvert \\text{OP(E12)}\\to 1.\\,+0.\\times 10^{-30}\\,\\mathrm{i},\\text{OP(E21)}\\to \\left(-0.03626734060947795145020244939-2.004237714666237867354326095\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,\\varphi ^2-\\left(1.522150083623538480912456055-0.2442047957313920727733393355\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,\\varphi +\\left(1.\\,+0.\\times 10^{-30}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right),\\text{nontrivial generator \\{a,b\\}}\\to \\left\\{2,1\\right\\},\\text{both $\\varphi$-dependent?}\\to \\mathrm{False}\\rvert\\!\\rangle",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
